Location: Geonoids cave<br>
<br>
What: quad kiting noids!<br>
<br>
thats right, quad those bad boys. yes its tricky and yes they have lots of HPs. what i do is i gather 4 of them up, or 3 if one spawns as a shaman. it gets to be tricky but the best wya i found was to invis and go look at your pulls and plan them before actually pulling them<br>
<br>
anyway, down to the nitty gritty. i get four and get em all rounded up and packed up and sanred on same timer. using pillar of LIGHTNING  i nuke them down to they are bout reayd to die, then i alert whoever is with me to finish them off as i gate and stone back to FM and go at it again.<br>
<br>
the first time we did this, the L59 wiz i had with me got almost 1/2 bub of blue exp PER PULL. 4 kills = right at / slightly more than 1/2 bub blue. we did this for 4 hours and he got 2 bubs yellow exp in NO time at all.<br>
<br>
good luck and get busy! <p><BR><BR><CENTER><B>-=Bromil Brimstone=-</B></CENTER><BR><CENTER><I>60 Sorceror of Tarew Marr</I></CENTER><BR><CENTER><I>Minions of Kaer Baar</I></CENTER></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarmok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Armok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/01 2:28:16 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good place to help PL yer friendly other wizzys:</span><hr size=1> This sounds like an excellent strategy, perhaps even for a tag team of wizards quadding in WL.  However, the Caster's Realm database has the geonid HP total listed as 15,000.  Either this is too high, or you've got a VERY impressing array of mana gear!<br>
<br>
- Armok Komra (Arics)<br>
59 wizard of Povar <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uselwynarcaneofluclin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Selwyn Arcane of Luclin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/29/01 6:09:02 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://shop.castersrealm.com/images/thumbnails/Thumb-MaleWizOriginal.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good place to help PL yer friendly other wizzys:</span><hr size=1> Damn that sounds like fun. I should talk my bud into doing this with me once I get PoL. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
